Privacy Policy for Matiki

Effective Date: 05.11.2023

Welcome to Matiki, the engaging math training application ("App") developed by Goran & Tia Zadro, which offers a variety of arithmetic challenges designed to improve mental math skills.

1. Information We Collect

a. Personal Information

We do not require users to provide personal information to download or use our App. Users can access all features without the need to create an account or log in.

b. Non-Personal Information

We may collect non-personal information about the usage and performance of our App, such as the number of downloads, app interactions, and preference settings. This information is aggregated and used solely for improving app functionality and user experience.

2. How We Use Information

The non-personal information we collect helps us to:

Enhance and optimize the user experience
Address technical issues and understand feature usage patterns
Improve the content and functionality of our App
3. Sharing of Information

We do not share any user information with third parties. As our App does not collect personal information, user data remains private and confidential.

4. Data Retention Policy

Since the App does not collect personal information, we have no need to store or retain data. Any non-personal information that is collected will be retained only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this privacy policy.

5. Children's Privacy

Matiki does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13. If a parent or guardian believes that the App has inadvertently collected such information, please contact us promptly so that we can take necessary actions.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at [Your Contact Information].
